2 Data Types In Java:

Primitives in Java (8)

	numeric:
			whole numbers (10, 2022)

				byte (-128 to 127)
				short (-32768 to 32767)
				int
				long

			decimal numbers (5.99, 90.01)

				float
				double

	non numeric:

			1 character(M, F, $, #)

				char

			true or false
			 	boolean

Non Primitives

			"John", "Test123"





